---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Refund Policy - OptyP" description="Refund Policy for OptyP professional resume and profile optimization services.">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12 max-w-4xl font-body">

    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Refund Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        At OptyP, we strive to deliver exceptional resume and profile optimization that meets your expectations. 
        If you are unsatisfied, please review the refund policy terms below.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-500">
        <p>Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Content -->
    <article class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-700 space-y-12">

      <section>
        <h2>Refund Eligibility</h2>
        <div class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-400">
          <p class="font-semibold mb-4">Refunds may be considered in the following cases:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li><strong>Timeframe:</strong> Requests made within <span class="bg-yellow-200 px-2 py-1 rounded font-semibold">7 days</span> of service delivery.</li>
            <li><strong>Service Issues:</strong> Undelivered services or unresolved quality concerns.</li>
            <li><strong>Non-Delivery:</strong> Failure to deliver on agreed timelines without notice.</li>
            <li><strong>Technical Errors:</strong> Critical errors impacting service functionality.</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="mt-6 bg-red-50 p-4 rounded-lg border border-red-200">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-red-800 mb-3">Services Not Eligible for Refund</h4>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1 text-sm text-red-700">
              <li>Services completed and customer approved.</li>
              <li>Change of personal preference post delivery.</li>
              <li>Dissatisfaction with job search results.</li>
              <li>Services used or accessed beyond 7-day period.</li>
              <li>Custom requests outside original package scope.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Refund Process</h2>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="bg-green-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-green-200">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-green-800 mb-4">Step-by-Step Refund Procedure</h3>
            <ol class="list-decimal pl-6 space-y-4 text-gray-700">
              <li>
                <strong>Submit Request:</strong> Contact us at <a href="mailto:info@optyp.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">info@optyp.com</a>.
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Provide Details:</strong> Include order number, package details, and refund reason.
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Review:</strong> Our team reviews your request within 5 business days.
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Resolution:</strong> We communicate our decision and process refund within 7-10 business days.
              </li>
            </ol>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-yellow-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-yellow-200">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-yellow-800 mb-3">Information Needed for Refund Requests</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-yellow-700">
              <li>Full name and email used for purchase</li>
              <li>Order/Transaction ID</li>
              <li>Purchased package/service type</li>
              <li>Detailed refund reason</li>
              <li>Supporting documents (if applicable)</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Alternative Solutions</h2>
        <div class="bg-purple-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-purple-200 text-purple-800">
          <p class="mb-4 font-semibold">Before requesting a refund, consider these options:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-3">
            <li><strong>Free Revisions:</strong> Two rounds included in all packages to address concerns.</li>
            <li><strong>Direct Support:</strong> Reach out to discuss and resolve your issues.</li>
            <li><strong>Consultation Call:</strong> Schedule a call to review deliverables.</li>
            <li><strong>Service Adjustments:</strong> Modify scope to better suit needs.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Refund Methods & Timeline</h2>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-4">Payment Methods and Refund Timing</h3>
          <div class="overflow-x-auto">
            <table class="w-full text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
              <thead>
                <tr class="border-b border-gray-300">
                  <th class="py-2 px-4 text-left font-semibold">Payment Method</th>
                  <th class="py-2 px-4 text-left font-semibold">Refund Timeline</th>
                  <th class="py-2 px-4 text-left font-semibold">Processing Fee</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr class="border-b border-gray-200">
                  <td class="py-2 px-4">Credit Card</td>
                  <td class="py-2 px-4">5-10 business days</td>
                  <td class="py-2 px-4">No fee</td>
                </tr>
                <tr class="border-b border-gray-200">
                  <td class="py-2 px-4">Debit Card</td>
                  <td class="py-2 px-4">3-7 business days</td>
                  <td class="py-2 px-4">No fee</td>
                </tr>
                <tr class="border-b border-gray-200">
                  <td class="py-2 px-4">Digital Wallets</td>
                  <td class="py-2 px-4">1-3 business days</td>
                  <td class="py-2 px-4">No fee</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td class="py-2 px-4">Bank Transfer</td>
                  <td class="py-2 px-4">3-5 business days</td>
                  <td class="py-2 px-4">May incur banking fees</td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Partial Refund Policy</h2>
        <p>Partial refunds may be issued upon review in cases such as:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>Partial delivery due to client unavailability</li>
          <li>Mid-project scope changes</li>
          <li>Issues limited to specific bundled services</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-600">
          Partial refund amounts are determined on a case-by-case basis and communicated during the review process.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Contact Section -->
      <section class="bg-blue-600 text-white p-8 rounded-lg text-center">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Need Assistance with a Refund?</h2>
        <p class="mb-6">Our dedicated support team is here to help resolve your refund concerns promptly.</p>
        <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:info@optyp.com" class="text-blue-200 hover:text-white underline">info@optyp.com</a></p>
        <p><strong>Contact Page:</strong> <a href="/contact/" class="text-blue-200 hover:text-white underline">Visit Our Contact Page</a></p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-blue-200 text-sm">Response times are typically within 24 hours on business days.</p>
      </section>

    </article>
  </div>
</Layout>
